Title: 调用关系图
Describe: 调用链重点展示模型调用、工具执行、子代理、队友协议和 MCP 工具池的跨边界关系。
------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
S06_CALL_RELATIONSHIPS: 主循环到工具执行

[Description]
主调用链从 CLI 或 cron autorun 进入 `agent_loop`，然后经 `call_llm`、`with_retry` 调用 Anthropic。

返回 tool_use 后，`trigger_hooks("PreToolUse")` 先检查权限，再按后台或同步路径执行 handler。

同步路径通过 `BUILTIN_HANDLERS` 或 MCP handler 调用具体函数。
[UML]
@startuml
participant "CLI 或 cron_autorun_loop" as Caller
participant "agent_loop" as Loop
participant "call_llm / with_retry" as Retry
participant "Anthropic API" as API
participant "HOOKS" as Hooks
participant "handlers" as Handlers
participant "background worker" as BG
Caller -> Loop: agent_loop(history, context)
Loop -> Retry: call_llm(messages, context, tools, state, max_tokens)
Retry -> API: client.messages.create
API --> Retry: response.content
Retry --> Loop: response
Loop -> Hooks: trigger_hooks(PreToolUse, block)
alt denied
  Hooks --> Loop: permission message
  Loop -> Loop: append denied tool_result
else run in background
  Loop -> BG: start_background_task(block, handlers)
  BG -> Handlers: call_tool_handler(...)
  Loop -> Loop: append placeholder tool_result
else synchronous
  Loop -> Handlers: call_tool_handler(handler, input, name)
  Handlers --> Loop: output string
  Loop -> Hooks: trigger_hooks(PostToolUse, block, output)
end
Loop -> Loop: append user tool_result content
@enduml

[Detail]
这张序列图强调顺序和责任交接。

`HOOKS` 发生在 handler 之前和之后，权限拒绝仍然被转成 tool_result 反馈给模型。

后台任务的真正输出不在当前轮返回，而是后续由 `collect_background_results` 生成 `task_notification`。

MCP 工具在序列图中归入 handlers，因为 `assemble_tool_pool` 已把 prefixed handler 合并到同一张 handler 表。

------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
队友计划审批调用链

[Description]
`spawn_teammate_thread` 内部注册 `submit_plan` 工具。

队友模型调用 `submit_plan` 时，`_teammate_submit_plan` 创建 `ProtocolState`，向 lead inbox 发送 `plan_approval_request`，并把 `protocol_ctx["waiting_plan"]` 设为 request id。

等待期间队友只轮询 inbox，不继续模型步骤，直到 lead 用 `review_plan` 发送 `plan_approval_response`。
[UML]
@startuml
participant "teammate model loop" as Mate
participant "_teammate_submit_plan" as Submit
participant "pending_requests" as Pending
participant "MessageBus" as Bus
participant "lead tools" as Lead
Mate -> Submit: submit_plan(plan)
Submit -> Pending: pending_requests[req_id] = ProtocolState
Submit -> Bus: send(plan_approval_request, req_id)
Submit --> Mate: Plan submitted (req_id)
Mate -> Mate: waiting_plan = req_id
loop approval gate closed
  Mate -> Bus: read_inbox(name)
end
Lead -> Bus: review_plan(request_id, approve, feedback)
Bus -> Mate: plan_approval_response
Mate -> Mate: waiting_plan = None
Mate -> Mate: append [Plan approved/rejected]
@enduml

[Detail]
该图回答“计划审批为什么真的是 gate”。

关键点是 `protocol_ctx["waiting_plan"]` 非空时，队友线程只 sleep 和检查 protocol reply，不调用模型继续任务。

风险是 pending request 没有过期时间，lead 如果永不回复，队友会一直等待直到外部 shutdown 或线程结束。

------------------------------------------------------------
